Resource Profile: Observation EXAM

Official URL: http://va.gov/fhir/StructureDefinition/ObservationEXAM Version: 1.5.11
Draft as of 2025-05-08 Computable Name: ObservationEXAM

This StructureDefinition contains the maps for VistA file V EXAM (9000010.13) to Observation.

​See also the FHIR Shorthand.

Use Case Overview

Usage:

  • This Resource Profile is not used by any profiles in this Implementation Guide
